sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Adapter
    participant Normalizer
    participant CDM as Canonical Data Model
    participant Service
    
    Client->>Adapter: Request data
    Adapter->>External API: Raw API call
    External API-->>Adapter: API-specific response
    Adapter->>Normalizer: Apply field mappings
    Normalizer->>CDM: Transform to canonical model
    CDM->>Service: Provide normalized data
    Service-->>Client: Return consistent response
    
    Note over Adapter,Normalizer: Field mapping & type conversion
    Note over Normalizer,CDM: Data enrichment & validation
    Note over CDM,Service: Business logic application
